<p>If you want to participate in the visual records process, or simply need SCP Fuel, feel free to click on the link below and join.</p>
<h2 id="toc12"><span><a href="http://visual-records.wikidot.com">» SCP Foundation Visual Records «</a></span></h2>
</div>
</div>

